dct_title_s: MTA Bronx bus map / MTA New York City Transit. (Map)
dct_description_sm: Includes text, index to points of interest, and color-coded bus-route directory. On verso: text, color-coded bus-route directory with time/frequency tables, outline map, and advertisements. "22-30-1384 5 4 3 2."
dct_publisher_sm: New York, NY : MTA New York City Transit, 2006.
